&lt;h2 id=&#34;development&#34;&gt;Development&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# run x-ray daemon locally (nodejs code sends trace data to it and it forwards it to aws x-ray service)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# see https://docs.aws.amazon.com/xray/latest/devguide/xray-daemon.html &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; ~/bin/aws-xray-daemon-macos-3.x
./xray_mac -o -n us-east-1 

&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# run code that generates trace/segment data&lt;/span&gt;
npm run dev
